Description: This is the dataset corresponding to the ItalWordNet as created at the Institute of Computational Linguistic "A. Zampolli" in Pisa.The resource contains single instances such as single synset and single word/wordsense and collective files to list all synsets and word(sense)s.The resource has been created according to the WN2.0 specification- http://www.w3.org/2006/03/wn/wn20/
